title: Tombspire: To the Caverns!
description:
Stream begins 8am EST and goes till 5pm EST

Ahh yes, my dwarves! Tombspire now has a competent military and the time has come to dig! 
What dangers lurk below? What light-starved terrors will we unleash?! Well, I suppose we shall see, now won't we?! Strike the earth!

Music by the frighteningly talented Ivan Duch: https://www.youtube.com/c/IvanDuch
